201cSatan\u00a0said: By Your might, O Lord, I will continue to mislead the children of Adam, as long as their souls are in their bodies. The Lord said: By My might and majesty, I will continue\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26385,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/05\/14\/mercy-allah-surpass-expectations\/","url_meta":{"origin":38343,"position":2},"title":"Ibn Mas&#8217;ud on Mercy: Allah&#8217;s forgiveness will surpass all expectations","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 14, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"'Awn ibn Abdullah reported: Abdullah ibn Mas'ud, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \"Allah Almighty will certainly forgive on the Day of Resurrection, with such forgiveness as has never been conceived by the heart of any person.\" Source:\u00a0H\u0323usn al-Z\u0323an billa\u0304h 66 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31836,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/08\/dua-ask-afwa-afiyah-akhirah\/","url_meta":{"origin":38343,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Ask Allah for pardon and wellness","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 8, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAsk your Lord for forgiveness and wellness in the world and the Hereafter. If you are given forgiveness and wellness in the world and the Hereafter, you have succeeded.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 3848 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1908,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/01\/29\/reconcile-cuts-you-off\/","url_meta":{"origin":38343,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Forbearance: Reconcile, forgive your wrongdoers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 29, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"'Uqbah ibn 'Amr reported: I met the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said to me, \u201cO 'Uqbah, reconcile with whoever cuts you off, give to whoever deprives you, and forgive whoever wrongs you.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 17452 Grade:\u00a0Hasan (fair) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064f\u0642\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0629\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":905,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/07\/06\/umar-mercy-pardon-forgiveness\/","url_meta":{"origin":38343,"position":5},"title":"Umar on Forgiveness: No mercy for the unmerciful, unforgiving","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 6, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Qabisah ibn Jabir reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be 